{
  "text": "The DSM expressions correspond to \"Winter-type\" design curves, which (i) were calibrated against a large number of experimental and/or numerical results, and (ii) prescribe that the column nominal strengths against local, distortional and global failure (P nl , P nd and P ng ) are given by Schafer [CITATION_1] ",
